div.div: Regression coefficients of the top models describing great tit local recruitment in relation to caterpillar biomass.
div.p: The regression coefficients (Î²) and SE for models describing local recruitment of the great tit derived from models E1, E3 and E5 in S11 Table. Coefficients are presented in the logit scale. Variables that had confidence intervals that do not include zero are in bold.
